name: Welcome to Our Party!
description:
This piece of art is the collaboration of Cartoon Culture x Bright Me To The Moon.

This is my collage artwork which is inspired from the joyful moments of being part of the H=N world. When I create an artwork and communicate with other amazing artists in this community, I am always pleased and excited as if i am in a party everyday.   

Hope you like this!
Have a wonderful time!

love,
